

Login as Docker user -->default path /home/docker
vagrant@ubuntu-xenial:~$ sudo su - docker
docker@ubuntu-xenial:~$ pwd
/home/docker

1.To list the containers

    $ docker ps
    
   To list the images
   
    $ docker image ls
    
2. If any container is running, you can run a command in that running container

    $ docker exec [OPTIONS] CONTAINER COMMAND [ARG...]
      See 'docker exec --help'.
      
      ex : $ docker exec -it relaxed_hodgkin /bin/bash --> this will create a bash session for the container
           bash-4.4# ls -lart -->you can view the file system structure of the container
           
3. Jenkins workspace path

    docker@ubuntu-xenial:/var/lib/jenkins/workspace$
    
  
    

           
